00:00:28.169 --> 00:00:29.849
## "What's your educational background?" Rodrigo,
Campo Grande, Brazil

00:00:29.849 --> 00:00:33.180
I went to school in New York where I earned
two college degrees, one in physics and one

00:00:33.180 --> 00:00:36.770
