00:00:38.830 --> 00:00:40.690
## "How long does it take to create a video?"
Tracey, Ohio

00:00:40.690 --> 00:00:44.800
I've tracked my time to get an accurate answer
and every minute of final video you see takes

00:00:44.800 --> 00:00:49.720
me between 10 and 20 hours of writing and
animating to make. So a typical 5 minute video

00:00:49.720 --> 00:00:52.450
is 50 to 100 hours of work.

00:00:52.450 --> 00:00:55.870
While that's a lot, it doesn't include the
research phase which is difficult to quantify

00:00:55.870 --> 00:00:59.929
-- some of the videos I've made I'd been collecting
notes on for more than a year before starting.

00:00:59.929 --> 00:01:01.680
## "What was you favourite video make?" Brittany
