00:01:23.990 --> 00:01:26.680
## "What is do you think should be in the
curriculum but isn't?" Jamaal, Arizona

00:01:26.680 --> 00:01:29.570
Computer programming. I was kind of shocked
and horrified when I started teaching in the

00:01:29.570 --> 00:01:32.799
UK to discover there were no real computer
programming lessons.

00:01:32.799 --> 00:01:35.909
