question is what to get rid of to make room

00:01:39.470 --> 00:01:42.990
for computer programming and, without the
slightest hesitation I'd ditch the foreign

00:01:42.990 --> 00:01:47.170
languages classes -- after all, computer programming
is getting us closer and closer to a universal

00:01:47.170 --> 00:01:48.159
translator anyway.

